<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The mhd_assert(...) statement is typically a debug-only check that expands to no code in release builds (e.g. to ((void)0) when assertions are disabled). In that configuration the statement has no effect and its removal would not change program behaviour, so the project contains dead code.
</scenario>

